OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1782915514
OL,3,CCan you save any money as energy price
OL,4,Ccap rises by 13%?
OL,6,FHousehold energy prices are set to
OL,7,Fremain high throughout this winter,
OL,8,Faccording to the latest forecasts
OL,9,Fahead of a #221 jump from Wednesday.
OL,11,FOfgem's price cap will rise by 13%, or
OL,12,F#18 a month, from July 1 to #1,862 a
OL,13,Fyear for the average household using
OL,14,Fboth electricity and gas, after the
OL,15,FMiddle East conflict sent global
OL,16,Fenergy costs soaring.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
