OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1782915514
OL,3,CCan you save any money as energy price
OL,4,Ccap rises by 13%?
OL,6,FEnergy costs rocketed after Iran
OL,7,Fresponded to US and Israel attacks by
OL,8,Fblocking the crucial Strait of Hormuz
OL,9,Fshipping route, through which a fifth
OL,10,Fof the world's oil and gas is carried.
OL,12,FThis month's interim peace deal has
OL,13,Fseen the vital route begin to reopen
OL,14,Fin recent days, which has helped bring
OL,15,Fdown oil and natural gas prices, with
OL,16,Fthe latter being a key driver of power
OL,17,Fbills in the UK.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31003
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1782915514
OL,3,CCan you save any money as energy price
OL,4,Ccap rises by 13%?
OL,6,FBut it still leaves a question mark
OL,7,Fover whether the government will
OL,8,Flaunch any targeted energy support for
OL,9,Fthe winter months.
OL,11,FITV News looks at a few ways in which
OL,12,Fyou could save some money ahead of the
OL,13,Fprice rise.
OL,15,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,16,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,17,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,18,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
