OL,3,CCan you save any money as energy price
OL,4,Ccap rises by 13%?
OL,6,FOne of the best ways to save money is
OL,7,Fto switch to a fixed tariff. By
OL,8,Flocking in rates now, you could
OL,9,Fprotect yourself from upcoming rises.
OL,11,FMany of the cheapest 12-month fixes
OL,12,Fare below the cap. However, experts
OL,13,Fwarn that you should compare the
OL,14,Fentire market before making a switch,
OL,15,Fchecking deals that are tied to your
OL,16,Fregion and level of usage.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
