OL,3,CCan you save any money as energy price
OL,4,Ccap rises by 13%?
OL,6,FTurning off standby appliances at the
OL,7,Fplug can save around #45 per year,
OL,8,Faccording to the Energy Saving Trust.
OL,9,FA way to monitor this is by using
OL,10,Fsmart plugs, which make them even
OL,11,Feasier to switch off.
OL,13,FLonger-term ways to cut household
OL,14,Fcosts can include lowering your boiler
OL,15,Fflow temperature - a reduction of its
OL,16,Fheating flow down to 55C or 60C will
OL,17,Fstill heat your home, but consume 8%
OL,18,Fless gas.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
