OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1782915514
OL,3,CCan you save any money as energy price
OL,4,Ccap rises by 13%?
OL,6,FWhile Ofgem is updating its definition
OL,7,Fof a typical consumer from July to
OL,8,Freflect falling household energy use,
OL,9,Fwhich adjusts the headline figure to
OL,10,F#1,654, Cornwall said this represented
OL,11,F"little change" on a like-for-like
OL,12,Fbasis.
OL,14,FDr Craig Lowrey, principal consultant
OL,15,Fat Cornwall Insight, said: "The Iran
OL,16,Fceasefire gave the markets some
OL,17,Fbreathing room but this is a pause,
OL,18,Fnot a resolution to the conflict.
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@OO]wD@\OU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31010
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1782915514
OL,3,CCan you save any money as energy price
OL,4,Ccap rises by 13%?
OL,6,F"What comes out of the final
OL,7,Fagreement, if there is one, will
OL,8,Fmatter enormously for energy prices.
OL,9,FAnd even in the best-case scenario,
OL,10,Fthe enduring effects from the conflict
OL,11,Fwill be with us for a while.
OL,13,F"Infrastructure takes time to repair,
OL,14,Fsupply chains take time to recover and
OL,15,Fhouseholds will be left dealing with
OL,16,Fthe consequences for some time."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUxD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
